description: Information about the eggs that are cryopreserved in a particular fertility treatment cycle.

columns.name: RECORD_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the cycle record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: CRYO_EGG_ID_NAME
columns.description: The custom ID title for the egg. If not set, the ID is based on the line number.

columns.name: CRYO_EGG_DATE
columns.description: The date of cryopreservation for eggs.

columns.name: CRYO_EGG_DAY
columns.description: The number of days of culture for the egg prior to cryopreservation.

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_STAGE_C_NAME
columns.description:
The cryopreserved egg's stage.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


1 Cell


2 Cell


3 Cell


4 Cell


5 Cell


6 Cell


7 Cell


8 Cell


More than 8


Morula


Early Blastocyst


Blastocyst


Full Blastocyst


Expanded Blastocyst


Hatching Blastocyst


Hatched Blastocyst


Unknown

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_GAMETE_SOURCE_C_NAME
columns.description:
The cryopreserved egg's source, such as autologous, partner, or donor.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


Autologous


Partner


Known Donor


Anonymous Donor


Mixed


Embryo Donor


Oocyte Contributor and Intended Parent

columns.name: CRYO_EMBRYO_GAMETE_STATE_C_NAME
columns.description:
The cryopreserved egg's state at the beginning of the cycle, such as fresh or thawed.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


Fresh


Thawed


Frozen Embryo


Not Applicable

columns.name: CRYOEGG_MATURITY_C_NAME
columns.description:
The cryopreserved egg's maturity.


May contain organization-specific values: Yes


 Category Entries: 


Metaphase 1


Metaphase 2


Germinal Vesicle


Atretic


Abnormal
